{"tid":1311313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街！TVB講上水個遊行嗰陣完全唔提反送中","createTime":"2019-07-13T06:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T09:03:39.000Z","uid":273803,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ab1b65b000f69ab81682f3b7e5f0829020feda99","tid":1311313,"uid":273803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:22:04.000Z","msg":"我啱啱睇CCTVB新聞台，講起上水遊行嗰節完全隻字不提反送中同埋五大訴求，講到好似一個普通反水貨客行動咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當中有一節訪問金金大師，個訪問亦只係好詳細咁講解點解要反水貨客。普通人睇完一定唔知知今日大家出嚟嘅初衷係反送中。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日喺上水嘅手足，如果要接受任何訪問，一定句句都要提住五大訴求。記住反水貨客只係支線任務。同埋唔好同水貨客有太多衝突，sidetrack 件事。"},{"pid":"fccff679bf4be8de959c1d4909e884770b82031d","tid":1311313,"uid":273803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:22:31.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"775d5f8108925148eb5b6e1ad08207ca8fba189e","tid":1311313,"uid":88013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:32:14.000Z","msg":"做得cctvb訪問唔係預咗佢會選擇性報導咩？"},{"pid":"ec83d63455aa131abff50749ba3a7635d111525c","tid":1311313,"uid":98958,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:37:42.000Z","msg":"岩岩「中華掠影」<br />\n講杭州某住宅區<br />\n自從裝咗cam圍住啲住宅 <br />\n少咗高空擲物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又幫監控燈柱打定底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dbc329474b8be6717175175bc85835a21237d91","tid":1311313,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec83d63455aa131abff50749ba3a7635d111525c","tid":1311313,"uid":98958,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T06:37:42.000Z","msg":"岩岩「中華掠影」<br />\n講杭州某住宅區<br />\n自從裝咗cam圍住啲住宅 <br />\n少咗高空擲物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又幫監控燈柱打定底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\"